# 🚗 Samad's Web Page

Samadning shaxsiy veb-sahifasi — mashhur avtomobillar kolleksiyasiga bag'ishlangan.

🌐 **Demo:** [samadswebpage.netlify.app](https://samadswebpage.netlify.app/)

---

## 📌 Loyiha haqida

Bu shaxsiy veb-sahifa bo'lib, unda Samadning sevimli avtomobillari (Bugatti, Nissan GT-R, Formula mashinalari va boshqalar) slider ko'rinishida namoyish etilgan.

---

## 🚀 Xususiyatlar

- 🔍 Qidiruv paneli
- 🖼️ Avtomobillar slider/karusel (oldingi / keyingi tugmalar)
- 🏎️ Bugatti, Nissan GT-R, Formula avtomobillari rasmlari
- 💬 Iqtibos (Quote) bo'limi
- 📱 Mobil qurilmalarga moslashtirilgan

---

## 🛠️ Texnologiyalar

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/) — hosting

---

## 📂 Loyihani ishga tushirish

```bash
# Repositoriyani klonlash
git clone https://github.com/samad/samads-webpage.git

# Papkaga kirish
cd samads-webpage

# index.html faylini brauzerda ochish
open index.html
```

